content.html:
With no one else to watch them while he attends a job interview, Donald Duck begrudgingly leaves his nephews Huey, Dewey and Louie with his uncle Scrooge McDuck, who has difficulty bonding with them. Webby Vanderquack, the granddaughter of Scrooge's housekeeper Mrs. Beakley, befriends the boys and shows them examples of Donald's heroics as Scrooge's sidekick, but they inadvertently release various ancient evils housed in the artifacts in Scrooge's garage.

Watched on Fire TV
